{"tid":149332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭清華：人大釋法是大石壓死蟹","createTime":"2017-03-09T08:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T08:25:50.000Z","uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"604745f085e743a3b4a8dfd4fe915c0ffe80cd08","tid":149332,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/03/09/1508728_4ace61cda1f70fb99fd743eda89b2d7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F1508728_4ace61cda1f70fb99fd743eda89b2d7d.jpg&h=9392141f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前中聯辦主任、現任廣西自治區黨書記彭清華表示，人大常委釋法是「大石壓死蟹」，振奮人心。<br />\n<br />\n廣西自治區黨委書記彭清華表示，中央出手一錘定音，它叫「大石壓死蟹」，這次就是「大石壓死蟹」，把「港獨」議員一下子就把他剝奪，而且法院也只能按照人大來判決，它有法律效力，還有幾個議員還在審，如果把這幾個「一鍋煮」了，這就做徹底了。最後還看法院怎麼判，這一次是非常振奮人心。<br />\n<br />\n彭清華早上出席廣西人大代表全體會議，會上討論人大常委會工作報告。彭清華離開時被問及對特首選舉的看法，他表示，港澳辦主任王光亞對特首標準已經說得很清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1508728/%E3%80%90%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E5%BD%AD%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%3A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%9F%B3%E5%A3%93%E6%AD%BB%E8%9F%B9+%E6%8C%AF%E5%A5%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1508728%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%258F%25AF%253A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%259F%25B9%2B%25E6%258C%25AF%25E5%25A5%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9ojOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=172eaf0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1508728/%E3%80%90%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E5%BD%AD%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%3A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%9F%B3%E5%A3%93%E6%AD%BB%E8%9F%B9+%E6%8C%AF%E5%A5%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83</a>"},{"pid":"c877555f56e89829f774e70a0b3c03bf60efbf10","tid":149332,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"證明共匪真係唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用貶義詞黎讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}